track_notes:
Uneventfull gravel road along the lake until reaching Osnabrücker Hütte (mountainhut). Staying overnight is recommened. Otherwise a quite long distance and about 1000 m ascent.
Nice path up to both Schwarzsee lakes. From the upper lake follow sporadic markings on rock to the southern summit and along the ridgeline to the summit.
Big boulders required attention. Technical difficulty I-II
